ntp server 10.8.90.2 prefer
!
patch panel
   patch VPWS-1033
      connector 1 interface Port-Channel100.1033
      connector 2 pseudowire ldp VPWS-1033
   !
   patch VPWS-23
      connector 1 interface Ethernet30.23
      connector 2 pseudowire ldp VPWS-23
   !
   patch VPWS-44
